---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BudgetingStyleQuiz from '../../components/BudgetingStyleQuiz.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';

const title = "Find Your Budget Type";
const description = 'Take this quick quiz to discover your budgeting personality and get personalized tips to improve your finances.';
---

<BaseLayout title={`${title} — ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={description}>
	<main>
		<article>
			<header class="quiz-header">
				<h1>Find Your Budget Type</h1>
				<p class="quiz-intro">Answer 7 quick questions about your money habits and we will match you with a budgeting style, along with a practical tip to help you improve.</p>
			</header>

			<BudgetingStyleQuiz />

			<section class="quiz-why">
				<h2>Why knowing your budget type matters</h2>
				<p>Most people struggle with budgeting not because they lack willpower, but because they are using an approach that does not match how they naturally think about money. A system built for a Planner will feel suffocating to a Spender. A minimal setup designed for an Avoider will leave a Saver wanting more detail.</p>
				<p>Understanding your type helps you pick the right tools and build habits that actually stick. Instead of forcing yourself into someone else's framework, you can start with strategies that work with your instincts, not against them.</p>
				<p>This quiz is not a diagnosis. It is a starting point. Once you know your tendencies, you can lean into your strengths and find small, practical ways to address the gaps. That is how real financial confidence gets built: one step at a time, in a way that feels like you.</p>
			</section>

			<div class="quiz-callout">
				<p class="quiz-callout-text">No matter your type, the right spreadsheet can help you stay on track. Browse all of our <a href="https://simplysheetdesign.etsy.com">budget templates</a> to find the one that fits how you manage money.</p>
			</div>
		</article>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.quiz-header {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
	}
	.quiz-header h1 {
		font-size: var(--text-h1);
		font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
	}
	.quiz-intro {
		font-size: var(--text-body);
		line-height: var(--leading-normal);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}
	.quiz-callout {
		margin-top: var(--space-xl);
		padding: var(--space-md);
		background: var(--color-bg-panel);
		border-radius: var(--radius-md);
	}
	.quiz-callout-text {
		font-size: var(--text-small);
		line-height: var(--leading-normal);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin: 0;
	}
	.quiz-callout-text a {
		font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
	}
	.quiz-why {
		margin-top: var(--space-xl);
	}
	.quiz-why h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-h2);
		font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
	}
	.quiz-why p {
		font-size: var(--text-body);
		line-height: var(--leading-normal);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}
</style>
